{"tid":387384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"行動不便老父買錯熱飲 18歲逆子擸拐杖打父母","createTime":"2017-09-04T14:51:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-04T15:43:45.000Z","uid":51649,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9acbf1fa93df02f1ab43bfae49dc83fae41a7404","tid":387384,"uid":51649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T14:51:34.000Z","msg":"沙田發生逆子打父母事件。昨晚11時許，水泉澳邨嶺泉樓一名18歲姓楊青年，叫83歲行動不便的老父替他落街買飯盒及凍飲。詎料老父回家後，青年發現父親買錯熱飲，他情緒激動，喝罵老父及母親(54歲)，並取起父親的拐杖襲擊兩老，兩老負傷逃至樓下大堂向保安員求助，由保安代為報案。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報到場，將姓楊青年拘捕，涉嫌襲擊致造成實際身體傷害。而受傷的兩老則由救護車送院治理。據悉，涉案的楊男於2016年時，曾涉嫌打傷母親。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170904&amp;guid=57168924&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170904%26guid%3D57168924%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=gcClyU5bevOxu1OoQd5TbwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=190a0f61\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170904%26guid%3D57168924%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=ecd8e04b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170904&amp;guid=57168924&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"1e018d23a46216a681c3625633fd1df47a893814","tid":387384,"uid":51649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T14:52:41.000Z","msg":"一開始以為蘋果做回帶西<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"470548eae5e0a4448071dc2f740ae77a9f4a178e","tid":387384,"uid":187,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T14:53:25.000Z","msg":"個老豆好撚慘"},{"pid":"be645796c2d70551d30eb4e38a1a1825afc01729","tid":387384,"uid":766,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T14:55:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個老豆好撚慘</blockquote><br />\n65 先學人生仔<br />\n個仔仲慘"},{"pid":"209d16f2dadd92be08cc3a681dd0649b8f151852","tid":387384,"